title: Joseph Joseph 30109 GoRecycle 14-liters (3.7 US Gallons) Recycling Portable Caddy, Small, Blue
features: Divided into two 7-liter (1.84 US Gallons) for easy separation. Total capacity 14-liters (3.7 US Gallons)
Lift lids to create a convenient carry handle
Easy to empty each side independently
Ideal for glass, paper, metal and plastic
description: We’re all conscious of the need to recycle more, but the extra effort to separate, compact and store trash and waste ready for collection can be a hassle and often creates more mess and clutter. That’s why Joseph Joseph created GoRecycle, a range of inventive products specifically designed to make home recycling quicker and easier. It’s easy to pre-sort, store and transport recycling with this smart, compact caddy. It’s divided into two 7-liter (1.84 US Gallons) compartments allowing you to separate different types of recycling - such as glass and paper - with lids that close to hide the contents of each side. These lids, when opened together, create a handle making it very easy to transfer recycling to a larger bin curbside or elsewhere. The two compartments can then be emptied independently by simply folding both lids to each side in turn, which traps the trash in one side as you empty the other. Capacity: 14-liters (3.7 US Gallons).
